## Critical Rules
- **NEVER use IVFFlat indexes** — always HNSW for vector search (see ARCHITECTURE.md)
- **Default similarity threshold is 0.1** — diverse thoughts have low cosine similarity
- **Deploy with --no-verify-jwt** — function handles its own auth via x-brain-key
- **Test after every change** — curl the function, verify results come back
- Always run `supabase functions deploy <name> --no-verify-jwt` after code changes

